{
  "id": 9051502051579,
  "title": "FAPO Single Turbo Manifold for Toyota Supra JZA80 Mk4 Lexus GS300 SC300 IS300 2JZGE T4",
  "handle": "fapo-single-turbo-manifold-for-toyota-supra-jza80-mk4-lexus-gs300-sc300-is300-2jzge-t4",
  "description": "<div>\n<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>1993-1998 Toyota Supra Mk4 JZA80 with 2JZ-GE 3.0L Naturally Aspirated Engine</li>\n<li>1993-2005 Lexus GS300 with 2JZ-GE 3.0L Naturally Aspirated Engine</li>\n<li>1992-2000 Lexus SC300 with 2JZ-GE 3.0L Naturally Aspirated Engine</li>\n<li>2001-2005 Lexus IS300 with 2JZ-GE 3.0L Naturally Aspirated Engine</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Notes:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>For single turbo conversion of 2JZ-GE engine ONLY; NOT direct fit</li>\n<li>Does NOT fit for 2JZ-GTE twin turbo engine</li>\n<li>Does NOT direct fit for stock non-turbo setup</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Holds boost up to 1000HP</li>\n<li>Fits T4 Divided (Twin Scroll) Turbo Flange and 40/50mm (4-bolt) Wastegate Flange</li>\n<li>Excellent quality and durability to improve vehicle performance; engineered to be bolt-on replacement for easy installation</li>\n<li>Ram style equal length turbo manifold, allows turbo spool faster and improves throttle response</li>\n<li>Tubular manifold design with better exhaust flow and delivers more top-end power</li>\n<li>Equal length runners for balanced exhaust reversion and enhanced turbo performance</li>\n<li>Flat 6-hole engine flanges, after special process shaping, more suitable for engine installation position</li>\n<li>Precision aligned tubes made of schedule 40 cast 304 stainless steel, 3 mm thick wall</li>\n<li>Head flanges laser-cut from high-quality 1/2-inch thick steel plates</li>\n<li>Flange flattened by hydraulic press for precise and leak-free sealing</li>\n<li>All joints golden color TIG brass style welded to prevent cracking and wear</li>\n<li>Flanges chrome plated for corrosion resistance</li>\n<li>Sandblasted surface for extra hardness</li>\n<li>Accessories shown in photos are included</li>\n<li>1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n<li>No instructions provided; professional installation recommended</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Manifold Type: Tubular Single Turbo Manifold</li>\n<li>Runner Diameter: 1-5/8 in. (42mm)</li>\n<li>Runner Layout: Equal Length</li>\n<li>Turbo Fitment: T4 Divided (Twin Scroll)</li>\n<li>Turbo Mount Position: Top Mount</li>\n<li>Wastegate Fitment: 40/50mm (4-bolt)</li>\n<li>Head Flange Thickness: 1/2 in. (13.5mm)</li>\n<li>Pipe Thickness: Schedule 40 (3mm)</li>\n<li>Material: 304 Stainless Steel</li>\n<li>Finish: Sandblasted</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
